sentences.english: A polling station is where I vote and is listed on my Elector Information Card.
sentences.chinese: 投票站是我前往投票的地方，在選民登記列明地點。

sentences.english: The payroll journals and the pay slips are missing regular working hours.
sentences.chinese: 工資表和工資條沒有列明正班工作時間。

sentences.english: Tariff quota concessions will be implemented according to the date specified in the "implementation" column.
sentences.chinese: 關稅配額減讓將按照“實施”欄中列明的日期實施。

sentences.english: Further terms and conditions as stated in relevant redemption Certificates apply.
sentences.chinese: 相關證書中列明的其他條款和條件將適用。

sentences.english: Please give details of the services the applicant has provided.
sentences.chinese: 請列明申請人曾參與的服務。

sentences.english: Documents listed in a credit should be presented as separate documents.
sentences.chinese: 信用證列明的單據應作爲單獨單據提交。

sentences.english: It's all written on the brochure price list. I believe there will be one right for you.
sentences.chinese: 售價表裏已經具體列明，我相信其中一定有適合你的。

sentences.english: Identify the item you've been spending so much money on.
sentences.chinese: 列明你在哪些項目上花了多少錢。

sentences.english: Lunch & Dinner which mentioned in itinerary.
sentences.chinese: 行程表內列明之午餐及晚餐。

sentences.english: The bill of lading must contain the name of actual port of discharge.
sentences.chinese: 提單列明具體的卸貨港是有必要的。

sentences.english: Checklist &specifications or relevant materials to be all listed in instruction documents.
sentences.chinese: 點檢清單及規格或相關資料都詳細列明在指引文件內。

sentences.english: Awards shall be made in accordance with the criteria and essential requirements specified in the tender documentation.
sentences.chinese: 應依照招標文件列明的標準和基本要求授予合同。

sentences.english: For serial notification, to provide the substance names of every notified substance.
sentences.chinese: 系列申報，應列明系列中各物質的名稱。

sentences.english: The enquiry is clearly stated with all relevant details at this stage.
sentences.chinese: 有關詢價項目和細則，均清楚列明。

sentences.english: The extent of insurance is stipulated in the basic policy form and in the various risk clauses.
sentences.chinese: 保險責任列明在基本保險條款和特別條款裏。

sentences.english: Unless otherwise specified, all programmes are of three-year duration.
sentences.chinese: 除列明之外，所有學士課程的修讀期爲三年。
